whatIsFullStackTemplateParagraph: Full-stack template is Spring/React based template that provides a set of functionalities needed for any web app.
supportedFunctionalitiesParagraph: Template supports basic functionalities that are needed for almost any web application. You can try each functionality for yourself by interacting with this webapp. You can either <loginLink>log in</loginLink> using Facebook, Google or Github or you can <signUpLink>sign up</signUpLink> and login using email and password.
reactParagraph:
The Frontend was written in React - a popular Javascript framework for making SPAs. It is fully integrated with Typescript and Redux. It also provides localization and dark/light theme support.

Much more information about this part and also whole source code can be found on Github
springBootParagraph:
Backend REST API was written in Spring using Spring boot. It uses double JWT based authentication, provides support for localization and also email sending.

Much more information about this part and also whole source code can be found on Github
